{"tid":569340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美製機械犬逃走遇阻識抵抗　網民大驚：智能叛變？","createTime":"2018-02-22T15:04:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T18:47:34.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fd1cb3731023ae8c7ff83f44d97262634a28266d","tid":569340,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T15:04:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180221/photo/bknint-20180221150510189-0221_17011_001_01p.jpg?20180222073632\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180221%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180221150510189-0221_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180222073632&h=0dd298b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n科技愈趨發達，人類不斷研發新型機械人，希望有助改善生活。美國一間科研公司研製了一部以四肢爬行、頭頸裝有機械臂的機械犬，它在逃出實驗室測試中遇到人類阻撓，不單沒有退縮，反而懂得靈巧地奮力抵抗，最終成功逃脫。公司本來是測試機械犬如何處理受干擾的情況，惟不少網民留言稱，擔心距離「智能叛變」一日不遠矣。 <br />\n<br />\n科技公司波士頓動力（Boston Dynamics）周二（20日）發放最新影片，可見機械犬「SpotMini」準備逃離實驗室，欲利用身上搭載的機械臂打開大門。此時工作人員以曲棍球棒用力壓住機械臂，阻撓它開門。機械犬沒有就此放棄，懂得退後辨識門把位置，成功抓緊門把打開大門。 <br />\n<br />\n不過工作人員繼續「出手」，用手頂住大門，機械犬隨即緊緊抓住門把不放，再因應其推門力道調整重心，用機械臂成功「反手」開門。在機械犬欲通過大門之際，工作人員再度出手用力推門，眼看就要把機械犬夾住，機械犬隨即轉動機械臂用力頂住大門，與工作人員鬥力，力保不失。 <br />\n<br />\n眼看機械犬快要成功通過測試，工作人員伸手拉住機械犬尾部有如尾巴的繩子，用力向後扯。然而機械犬未有放棄，即使腳步踉蹌仍能保持平衡，不斷掙扎向前跑，最後成功逃走。整個測試中，工作人員分別在最初及中段向機械犬發送了2次「前進」的指示，其餘所有動作均由它自動執行。<br />\n<br />\n片段上載至互聯網後，網民非但不太欣賞機械犬敏捷的身手，反而擔憂它太過「聰明」。有人留言道：「你希望發生機械人叛變嗎？現在正是。」亦有網民表示，研製這些產品並非為人解決問題，反而會製造問題，並質疑該公司在生產時有沒有任何道德規範。"},{"pid":"eb77859f53628656d44a3d1e0fec36daa1d8b6c1","tid":569340,"uid":42848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T15:06:31.000Z","msg":"metalhead<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ee8b1a63d99dd9c0fd756c2a81ca73caef382b","tid":569340,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T15:09:07.000Z","msg":"道德規範<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd7e5cc38a33c65a5d29cf09153ff0532555558","tid":569340,"uid":69484,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T15:09:15.000Z","msg":"成本降低左再講啦 <br />\n擔心呢d 笑死人"},{"pid":"8f6a79ab85797f412d1de9176a87e0f0da5de748","tid":569340,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eb77859f53628656d44a3d1e0fec36daa1d8b6c1","tid":569340,"uid":42848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T15:06:31.000Z","msg":"metalhead<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T15:27:21.000Z","msg":"我都諗起black mirror<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949d55538afc29bc523dd5040050279800a0e69b","tid":569340,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T15:30:18.000Z","msg":"it's skynet <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed5f58967bd46dc041bea8f11274e9d88d46abe","tid":569340,"uid":27706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T19:12:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>metalhead<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>我都諗起black mirror<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個集好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb6d57b11cfc2b0c7361dc89af3a77233fdba8c","tid":569340,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T17:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c922516ebd4dc1dca13487fe08c1c9f9fc4091","tid":569340,"uid":106375,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T17:50:37.000Z","msg":"機械犬都有權利學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3935db1899b3497bddcd04c391dbc3fe628d81","tid":569340,"uid":155019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T18:12:53.000Z","msg":"Metal gear <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9bcb4f3f0776bda67fbd5b33e076ad5f591f3a","tid":569340,"uid":116364,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T18:36:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a13cb2e3071995e3a7bbaf752ad33c953a266321","tid":569340,"uid":45232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bb9bcb4f3f0776bda67fbd5b33e076ad5f591f3a","tid":569340,"uid":116364,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T18:36:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T18:47:34.000Z","msg":"咁仲洗咩研發"}]}